No joke, we’re committed to delight you, even when you have a problem.Ashish, ApoorvFounders, RoadGodsDescribe your products in three words.Agile. Resolute. Protector~ The RoadGods' Story ~Apoorv was an engineer with Adobe Systems, an innovator at heart. His road trips revealed a ton of problems with the existing products.He discovered that products are designed for the “usage”, not for the “user”. Embarked on the journey to solve problems, create unique experiences for the users. Named the phenomenon - ‘RoadGods’. Ashish had just graduated from IIM Indore. Left his job offers to be a RoadGods instead. The duo has since led RoadGods to bring about disruption with its product innovations. The RoadGods holds multiple patents across continents for their innovations. And there's much more to come. Stay tuned.How did you come up with the idea for this product?Well, by now you know how our previous descendant, “The Ghost”, was born. The Ghost went on to redefine the norms and haunt the stereotypes.With Zarc, “Gods” have reconstructed the design DNA and are introducing a different series of Theft-slayer backpacks.For the unaware, Here’s the story :We observed a huge number of commuters face the problem of thefts every day. Many travelers wear their bags in front to avoid the thieves around. Thieves cut through the bags with a razor and steal valuables. Or simply, just open the zipper to pull out the stuff of their choice.Do you know that stealing from a backpack is much easier than picking pockets as a pocket is still very much in direct body contact whereas a backpack has several layers of stuff which do not let a person feel a hint of what happened behind their back?Not just commuters in public transport, even Riders are also much prone to this. What’s more, to make a thief's job much easier, many people forget to close their zippers. :)This pulled our attention to this huge vulnerability we travel with. Everyday!What makes your product special?Anointed Knight of the Gods, protector of your realm.“The Zarc is your Knight.Forged to be agile.Built to endure.Able to conquer.Nothing holds it down.”The Zarc comes with a shield inspired unibody design. A precision construction retains its unique form while giving flexibility resulting in better performance.What has been the best part of your experience?We've been hearing stories from our customers about how Ghost has been making their presence felt in public. How people have been hovering around Ghost to understand what this thing actually is. And when they come to know what it actually is, they are no less than amazed. This is what enthralls us each day. There, of course, have been feedback and suggestions from users which we have proactively addressed and that's how Ghost grows stronger each day. Thank you for this enthralling love!
